subject: Not what you want to see
body: [ https://go.bobcasey.com/go/182?t=1001&akid;=4743%2E552475%2EOvvHpE ]BobCasey for Senate This isn’t what you want to see, Peter. Another public polljust released shows Bob behind David McCormick. It’s the second one in twoweeks with us trailing. That’s the first time we’ve seen two back-to-backpolls with us down. You probably didn’t wake up this morning thinking “Gee,I’m going to donate to Bob Casey.” But with only 5 days left, we’re asking ifyou can chip in before it’s too late. Pennsylvania will come down to just ahandful of votes. We made you a personal link so we can thank everyone whodonates: [ https://secure.actblue.com/donate/casey-em-20241031-8?refcode=em20241031-8&refcode2;=4743_552475_OvvHpE&akid;=4743%2E552475%2EOvvHpE]https://secure.actblue.com/donate/casey-em-20241031-8?refcode=em20241031-8-dpwillis67@gmail.com We always knew thisrace would come down to the wire. We’ve been saying that on the campaign trailfor months — even when some pundits thought otherwise. Republican super PACsflooded the state with more than $150 million worth of attack ads. On Tuesday,control of the U.S. Senate and the White House will be decided right here inPennsylvania. Can we count on your help one last time? Please, use thispersonalized link to contribute now: [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/casey-em-20241031-8?refcode=em20241031-8&refcode2;=4743_552475_OvvHpE&akid;=4743%2E552475%2EOvvHpE]https://secure.actblue.com/donate/casey-em-20241031-8?refcode=em20241031-8-dpwillis67@gmail.com With polls this close,it’s no exaggeration to say your donation could be the difference betweenvictory and defeat. So, thanks in advance for all your support. Withgratitude, Team Casey To receive texts from Team Casey text TEAM to 51041.This email was sent to dpwillis67@gmail.com. Email is a critical way wecommunicate with grassroots supporters like you.
